      "content": "i just don't see the point anymore. everything i worked for in the lab... the last three years... just gone. the funding was pulled and my advisor won't even look me in the eye. i feel like i've spent my whole life building a version of myself that doesn't even exist if i'm not a researcher. i am just so incredibly tired of fighting for something that clearly doesn't want me.",
